msgstr "¿Qué hay en un flujo de trabajo?"

#: ../workflow/introduction.rst:37
msgid "Workflows Control"
msgstr "Control de flujos de trabajo"

#: ../workflow/introduction.rst:39
msgid "What ``states`` and ``transitions`` are available"
msgstr "¿Qué ``estados`` y ``transiciones`` están disponibles"

#: ../workflow/introduction.rst:40
msgid ""
"Which ``permissions`` will be managed (permissions not managed are left untouched from "
"their current value by the workflow)"
msgstr ""
"¿Cuáles ``permisos`` se administrarán (los permisos no administrados se dejan intactos "
