#: ../workflow/introduction.rst:41
msgid "Which ``groups`` will be managed (see ``states`` below for more about this)"
msgstr ""
"¿Cuáles ``grupos`` se administrarán (consulte ``estados`` a continuación para obtener "
"más información sobre esto)?"

#: ../workflow/introduction.rst:42
msgid ""
"Which ``variables`` will be tracked by the workflow (values are set and stored every "
