#: ../workflow/local-roles.rst:18
msgid ""
"Local roles give users (or groups) extra permissions in a very specific context. For "
"example, you may have two groups: pirates and ninjas."
msgstr ""
"Los roles locales otorgan a los usuarios (o grupos) permisos adicionales en un contexto "
"muy específico. Por ejemplo, puede tener dos grupos: piratas y ninjas."

#: ../workflow/local-roles.rst:21
msgid ""
"The ninjas probably don't want the pirates mucking about with their content. In this "
