"anything to this folder. Similarly, if only the pirate captain should have access to a "
"folder, add the pirate captain user to the sharing tab and select the correct "
"permission."
msgstr ""
"Es probable que los ninjas no quieran que los piratas jueguen con su contenido. En este "
