msgstr "Funcionamiento interno de Placeful Workflow"

#: ../workflow/placeful-workflow.rst:47
msgid ""
"This works by providing a more specific ``adapter`` for the ``IWorkflowChain`` "
"interface defined by DCWorkflow."
