#: ../workflow/roles-and-permissions.rst:143
msgid ""
"Security checks using ``zope.security.checkPermission()`` use the Zope 3 permission id"
msgstr ""
"Las comprobaciones de seguridad mediante ``zope.security.checkPermission()`` utilizan "
